.first # comment following key prior to value
  this is a value without newline

.first-newlines # comment following key prior to value
  this is a value with newline
  this seconds line should end in newline also

.second
  this is a value but
  it ends with and includes newlines

.third 
  the first char after the key is ' ' not a newline,
  but it should still be in RespectNewlinesMode

.fourth

  this is a value that starts with several newlines
  but it shouldn't have a starting newline

